86
00:04:13,462 --> 00:04:15,672
<i>Pink juga ikut bersenang-senang</i>

87
00:04:25,015 --> 00:04:27,851
Chloe, situasinya ternyata berbeda
dari yang kita bayangkan.

88
00:04:27,935 --> 00:04:28,936
SELAMAT DATANG KEMBALI

89
00:04:29,019 --> 00:04:32,064
-Mereka senang melihat kita.
-Menurutmu begitu?

90
00:04:32,147 --> 00:04:34,733
-Permisi, Putri.
-Kenapa mereka datang?

91
00:04:34,816 --> 00:04:37,027
Itu Luis Madrigal dan Robbie Hood.

92
00:04:37,110 --> 00:04:38,320
Kenapa tersenyum lebar?

93
00:04:38,904 --> 00:04:41,031
<i>P-R-I-N-C-E-S-S-S</i>

94
00:04:41,114 --> 00:04:43,659
<i>Ini dua putri favorit kami</i>

95
00:04:43,742 --> 00:04:45,327
<i>Sebut kami sangat diberkati</i>

96
00:04:45,410 --> 00:04:47,371
<i>Jelas kami bergaul dengan yang terbaik</i>

97
00:04:47,454 --> 00:04:49,414
Dua calon pahlawan sedang berproses

98
00:04:49,498 --> 00:04:51,583
<i>-Tiga!</i>
<i>-Aku tahu kau akan mengambil</i>

99
00:04:51,667 --> 00:04:53,126
<i>Mewarisi sifat kedua ibumu</i>

100
00:04:53,210 --> 00:04:55,254
<i>Menjaga kerajaan tetap kuat</i>

101
00:04:55,337 --> 00:04:56,380
<i>Membosankan!</i>

102
00:04:56,463 --> 00:04:57,881
<i>Lagi-lagi bocah-bocah manja</i>

103
00:04:57,965 --> 00:05:00,509
<i>Sopan dan anggun</i>
<i>Wanita-wanita cantik</i>

104
00:05:00,592 --> 00:05:02,135
<i>Kebanggaan kelas atas</i>

105
00:05:02,219 --> 00:05:04,555
Putri-putri sempurna, bayi-bayi nepotisme

106
00:05:04,638 --> 00:05:06,682
-Sopanlah, Hatter.
-Hatter?

107
00:05:07,558 --> 00:05:09,476
<i>Niat baik</i>

108
